data.description: Hurry on this lovely 4-BR home located in the desirable Fairway Woods community! Numerous upgrades including: remodeled kitchen (2020) with custom cabinets, countertops and tile backsplash. Vinyl plank flooring was installed in the living rm, dining rm, kitchen, laundry rm and all 3 bathrooms (2019).  Seller also had new carpeting installed on the stairs, hallway and bedrooms (2019).  Not to mention gorgeous new light fixtures in the living rm, kitchen, dining rm, hallway and Primary bedroom (2023).  Spacious bedrooms and the 2 full baths both have double vanities. The garage door was replaced in 2018.  This low maintenance, move-in ready home, will not last long!
